data.description: Great family home in Platntation Oaks.  Roof was replaced in  2016.  Home is located on a Private Cul-de-sac lot in a great, convenient location.  Flood Zone X - Never Flooded.  Refrigerator and window treatments remain.  Covered patio. Updated kitchen cabinets and countertops, New laminate floors throughout.  3 year old 15 x 30 in ground gunite pool.  Whole house Generac generator.  Fully fenced yard.  Plastic shed in pool area is reserved.
